reviewText: My grandchildren love "The Pond" stories and I love the great lessons they teach. We were happy with the quick time in getting the CD.

Seller sent this DVD to me scratched and cracked. It didn't play all the way through and when i was trying to play it, it kept skipping...why would they allow someone to pay for something like this? left a message with the seller to return this item and i have not heard back. STAY AWAY

Thanks
Sharon
